title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - US army Huey helicopter
description:
In this video we will look at the US army Huey helicopter which has been released today. The helicopter is still under development as we speak and to be honest there is still a lot of work to do.

If you also want to give the Huey helicopter a try download it from the site below:
